model.oplusplus

Class ObjectPlusPlus

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.oplusplus.ObjectPlus
      • model.oplusplus.ObjectPlusPlus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Discount, Event, Movie, Person, Room, RoomReservation, Seat, Ticket

    public abstract class ObjectPlusPlus
extends ObjectPlus
implements java.io.Serializable
    The class which simplifies connections between objects. Because it inherits from the ObjectPlus, it also helps with extent management.
